   </crs:Group>
   <crs:Description>
    <rdf:Alt>
     <rdf:li xml:lang="x-default">RAW infrared starting point: white balance floored at 2000K (Lightroom's minimum — the app goes further), tint toward green, gentle tone recovery and colour lift. Apply to NEF/DNG, then fine-tune Temp/Tint.</rdf:li>
    </rdf:Alt>
   </crs:Description>
